query:
SELECT 
  p.id,
  p.apiId,
  a.name as apiName,
  s.name as serviceName,
  s.smshubCode,
  p.ourPrice
FROM prices p
LEFT JOIN sms_apis a ON p.apiId = a.id
LEFT JOIN services s ON p.serviceId = s.id
WHERE p.countryId = 1 AND p.apiId = 1 AND p.active = 1
LIMIT 5;
